title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Youre always at a humble beginning if youre committed to your own evolution. Luckily, you're likely dedicated to the process of self-development now. But you may be uncomfortable in a situation that puts you at a novice level or requires starting over with some part of your life. However, you stall your own growth if you hold onto the familiar too long. But if youre willing to surrender to the demands of the current moment, you can experience it as the beginning of a victory story. Perseverance is the way of the peaceful warrior.
